title: Black Kiss TPB [alieneye] [h33t]
description:
Black Kiss was originally published by Vortex in the late eighties.  A 12 issue limited series written and drawn in B&W by Howard Chaykin, it was so full of sex and violence it had to be released in bags like a porno mag so that non-mature readers wouldn&#039;t corrupt their little minds.  Don&#039;t mistake this for porn though. It reads like like an uncensored hard-boiled film noir.  This lost gem is represents the peak of Howard&#039;s abilities. 

Normally I include a link for description, but this one reads better if you have no idea what&#039;s going on.

Many thanks to the original scanners.

Enjoy.
